&gt;
&gt; or
&gt;
&gt; /yourpath/heritrix-1.2.0/bin/arcreader /yourpath/heritrix-1.2.0/jobs/
&gt; yourjobname/arcs/******.arc &gt; ****.cdx
&gt;
&gt; Arc file format:
&gt; http://www.archive.org/web/researcher/ArcFileFormat.php
&gt; http://pages.alexa.com/company/arcformat.html
&gt;
&gt; cdx file format:
&gt; http://www.archive.org/web/researcher/example_cdx.php
&gt;
&gt; Then you may use the offset info in cdx file to access each uri file
&gt; the arc saved.
&gt;
&gt; The command is like:
&gt; /yourpath/heritrix-1.2.0/bin/arcreader --offset=438731 /yourpath/
&gt; heritrix-1.2.0/jobs/yourjobname/arcs/******.arc.gz
&gt;
&gt; Good luck!
